   <conbody>
      <table id="table_usq_zqk_lcc" class="- topic/table ">
         <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="danger" id="note_ffy_grk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock! </b>Contact  with  live  components  poses a
                           risk  of  serious  injury  or  even  death! </p>
                        <ul id="ul_ibt_jrk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, switch off the electric power supply. Follow
                              plant requirements for lockout tagout.</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="danger" id="note_ts2_3rk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Life threatening hazard due to a falling vertical carriage! </b>The
                           unsecured  vertical carriage  can  fall  down and  cause  serious injury
                           or even death!<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "/>
                        </p>
                        <ul id="ul_vyk_krk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Always make sure that the safety bolts of the vertical carriage are
                              properly installed before carrying out work on / near the
                              carriage!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note id="note_z2q_brk_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of injury from improperly performed maintenance!</b> Improper
                           maintenance can result  in  serious  personal  injury or material
                           damage!</p>
                        <ul id="ul_rrs_prk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, ensure that you have sufficient space!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Handle open, sharp-edged components with care!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Pay attention to cleanliness and orderliness at the place of work!
                              Loose components and tools lying around are a potential cause of
                              accidents!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Install all components correctly. Observe the prescribed bolt
                              tightening torques! Secure the bolts with bolt locking com- pound
                              (e.g. Weicon AN 302-43 (blue)) “medium strength”!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Secure components so that they cannot fall down or fall over!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Operating elements of the Emergency Stop system must be freely
                              accessible!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Operate the machine only when all the safety devices, e.g. safety
                              fence, light barriers and safety bolts are installed and fully
                              functional!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="warning" id="note_qty_brk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury from stored pneumatic energy! </b>Pneumatic energy may
                           be stored in the machine that can lead to uncontrolled movements of
                           components and injuries!</p>
                        <ul id="ul_ygd_xrk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout of the system. Only
                              thenstart the maintenance work!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="warning" id="note_zvd_crk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of crushing!</b> There are several  crushing  points on  the
                           machine that can cause injuries!</p>
                     </note>
                     <ul id="ul_mry_zrk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Do not reach between the following points: </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the steel housing</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the lifting mast</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">the locking pins and the container</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the horizontal carriage!</li>
                     </ul>
                     <ul id="ul_qdq_1sk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">No person is allowed inside the safety fence area when the machine is
                           switched on!</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="warning" id="note_dqk_crk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger due to non-observance of the prohibition of transporting
                              persons!</b> The MSK transfer system can pose a serious risk in the
                           event of  non-compliance and/or circumvention of the prohibition of
                           trans-  porting persons.</p>
                        <ul id="ul_a5n_35k_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Only operate the transfer system when all safety devices are in place
                              and in proper working condition, such as the programmed safety
                              interlocks and physical E-Stops. </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">No persons are allowed on the transfer system!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="warning" id="note_v5s_crk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury due to stored hydraulic energy!</b> Hydraulic energy
                           can be stored  in the  machine and cause the un-controlled  movement  of
                           components, which can  lead  to severe in-  juries!</p>
                     </note>
                     <ul id="ul_b31_25k_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Switch off the MSK system, as explained in this document.</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Do not begin maintenance work until then!</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note type="warning" id="note_fbv_crk_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury due to laser radiation!</b> Laser  radiation can cause
                           serious eye damage.</p>
                     </note>
                     <ul id="ul_iwh_15k_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Do not look into the laser beam!</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">If it is not possible to avoid looking directly into the laser beam
                           (e.g., during maintenance work), suitable eye protection must be
                           worn.</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <note id="note_etz_crk_lcc" type="caution" class="- topic/note ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock!</b>  Parts  of  the  machine may still be
                           live even when the emergency stop switch has been pressed! </p>
                        <ul id="ul_jzz_xtk_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Do not touch live parts and leads!</li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Observe the instructions in the operating manual!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </note>
                  </entry>
               </row>
